    <main>
        <section class="section">
            <div class="container p-0">
                <div class="row align-items-center m-0 p-0">
                    <div class="col-12 col-md-6 p-4 p-lg-2 mr-lg-0 order-2 order-md-1">
                        <h1>Adorned</h1>
                        <p class="text-justify">Adorned is a website that allows you to store your outfits and then just access them through your phone so you can choose what to wear without the need to look at your closet.</p>
                        <p class="text-justify">Adorned also helps you with matching your clothes by displaying them on top of each other so you can choose what to wear and if they go good together.</p>
                        <p><a href="/register" class="btn btn-primary">Register Now</a></p>
                        <p class="text-justify">If you want to know more please go <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 12 12" width="12" height="12">
