                    </div>
                    <div class="col-12 col-md-6 m-0 p-0 align-self-center text-center order-1 order-md-2">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="384" height="384" class="sec-pic"><path fill-rule="evenodd" fill="#007bff" d="M12 2.5a5.5 5.5 0 00-3.096 10.047 9.005 9.005 0 00-5.9 8.18.75.75 0 001.5.045 7.5 7.5 0 0114.993 0 .75.75 0 101.499-.044 9.005 9.005 0 00-5.9-8.181A5.5 5.5 0 0012 2.5zM8 8a4 4 0 118 0 4 4 0 01-8 0z"></path></svg>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>


        <section class="section" id="section-2">
            <div class="container p-0">
                <div class="row align-items-center m-0 p-0">
                    <div class="col-12 col-md-6 m-0 p-0 align-self-center text-center">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="384" height="384" class="sec-pic"><path fill-rule="evenodd" fill="#007bff" d="M6 9V7.25C6 3.845 8.503 1 12 1s6 2.845 6 6.25V9h.5a2.5 2.5 0 012.5 2.5v8a2.5 2.5 0 01-2.5 2.5h-13A2.5 2.5 0 013 19.5v-8A2.5 2.5 0 015.5 9H6zm1.5-1.75C7.5 4.58 9.422 2.5 12 2.5c2.578 0 4.5 2.08 4.5 4.75V9h-9V7.25zm-3 4.25a1 1 0 011-1h13a1 1 0 011 1v8a1 1 0 01-1 1h-13a1 1 0 01-1-1v-8z"></path></svg>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-12 col-md-6 p-4 p-lg-2">
                        <h1>How it works</h1>
                        <p class="text-justify">Our site stores the pictures on our database and pictures can be only accessed by your username and <strong class="text-light bg-primary rounded pr-1 pl-1">Validation Token</strong> that is given to you upon after every login.</p> 
                        <p class="text-justify">If you haven't logged on your pictures will not be available due to the validation token missing.</p>
                        <p><a href="#section-3" class="badge badge-primary">NEXT SECTION</a></p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>




        <!-- Section 3 -->
        <section class="section" id="section-3">
            <div class="container p-0">
                <div class="row align-items-center m-0 p-0">
                    <div class="col-12 col-md-6 mr-lg-0 order-2 order-md-1 p-4 p-lg-2">
                        <h1>Upload</h1>
                        <p class="text-justify">To upload pictures of your clothes, just take a picture of all your clothes first.</p>
                        <p class="text-justify">Then one by one upload them in the upload tab doing the following steps:</p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Season: Warm or Cold</li>
                            <li>Type: Shirt, Pants, or shoes</li>
                            <li>File: Choose photo</li>
                        </ul>
                        <p><a href="#section-4" class="badge badge-primary">NEXT SECTION</a></p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-12 col-md-6 m-0 p-0 align-self-center text-center order-1 order-md-2">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="384" height="384" class="sec-pic"><path fill-rule="evenodd" fill="#007bff" d="M2.25 4a.25.25 0 00-.25.25v15.5c0 .138.112.25.25.25h3.178L14 10.977a1.75 1.75 0 012.506-.032L22 16.44V4.25a.25.25 0 00-.25-.25H2.25zm3.496 17.5H21.75a1.75 1.75 0 001.75-1.75V4.25a1.75 1.75 0 00-1.75-1.75H2.25A1.75 1.75 0 00.5 4.25v15.5c0 .966.784 1.75 1.75 1.75h3.496zM22 19.75v-1.19l-6.555-6.554a.25.25 0 00-.358.004L7.497 20H21.75a.25.25 0 00.25-.25zM9 9.25a1.75 1.75 0 11-3.5 0 1.75 1.75 0 013.5 0zm1.5 0a3.25 3.25 0 11-6.5 0 3.25 3.25 0 016.5 0z"></path></svg>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>


        <!-- Section 4 -->
        <section class="section" id="section-4">
            <div class="container p-0">
                <div class="row align-items-center m-0 p-0">
                    <div class="col-12 col-md-6 m-0 p-0 align-self-center text-center">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="384" height="384" class="sec-pic"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M.408 15.13a2 2 0 01.59-2.642L17.038 1.33a2 2 0 012.85.602l2.828 4.644a2 2 0 01-.851 2.847l-17.762 8.43a2 2 0 01-2.59-.807L.408 15.13zm5.263-4.066l7.842-5.455 2.857 4.76-8.712 4.135-1.987-3.44zm-1.235.86L1.854 13.72a.5.5 0 00-.147.66l1.105 1.915a.5.5 0 00.648.201l2.838-1.347-1.862-3.225zm13.295-2.2L14.747 4.75l3.148-2.19a.5.5 0 01.713.151l2.826 4.644a.5.5 0 01-.212.712l-3.49 1.656z"></path><path d="M17.155 22.87a.75.75 0 00.226-1.036l-4-6.239a.75.75 0 00-.941-.278l-2.75 1.25a.75.75 0 00-.318.274l-3.25 4.989a.75.75 0 001.256.819l3.131-4.806.51-.232v5.64a.75.75 0 101.5 0v-6.22l3.6 5.613a.75.75 0 001.036.226z"></path></svg>
