                    <div class="col-12 col-md-6 p-4 p-lg-2">
                        <h1>How to view</h1>
                        <p class="text-justify">To be able to choose what you want to wear from your collection, you need to go to the choose tab.</p> 
                        <p class="text-justify">Choose the season you want to wear, then choose the type of clothing you want to wear, then click on the picture you want to wear.</p>
                        <p><a href="/register" class="btn btn-primary">Register Now</a><a href="/login" class="btn btn-primary ml-3">Login</a></p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
